title: #86: The Annunaki with Marshall Klarfeld
description:
Thank you for tuning into another episode of Tin Foil Hat With Sam Tripoli. Today Ryan and Dummy welcome from Ancient Aliens, Marshall Klarfeld. This episode we discuss...
1) Marshall Klarfeld and his many books he authored.
2)Origins of the Ancient Aliens story
3)The Cuneiform Texts
4)Niburu
5)Shiva's Hand Bag, watches and pinecone
6) Chaco Canyon
​Thank you for all of your support.
